  "titles": "Erebus The Dark Apostle, Emissary of the Warmaster, Child of the Primordial Truth",
  "lore": "As First Chaplain of the Word Bearers Legion, when the Emperor chastised Lorgar for worshipping him as a god, it was Erebus who counselled that if the Emperor was not worthy of Lorgar’s veneration, then there were other, older powers that were. The Primarch would have declared his new-found revelation to the entire galaxy there and then, but it was Erebus again who counselled caution, for he had his own plans. Erebus also set in motion a chain of events that led to the damnation of Horus revealing himself as the instrument of the ruination of all that the Emperor fought for and the ultimate pawn of the powers of the Warp.",
